modName: Ini files for RealVision ENB with Video tutorial
summary:
Ini files for RealVision ENB

Those are ini presets for RealVision ENB. also known as EWIs inis but I corrected the fGamma to 1.2400

*See video tutorial for installation.

Download includes:
Skyrim.ini
SkyrimPrefs.ini

To install go to:

Start/Document/My games/Skyrim
